data.title: Marines TV
data.meta_description: Marines and sailors with 2nd Medical Battalion conducted a field exercise Sep. 21-25, 2015, on Camp Lejeune, N.C. Service members from the battalion conducted casualty evacuation drills, and assembled a shock trauma platoon. (U.S. Marine Corps video by Cpl. Ryan Young and Lance Cpl. Immanuel Johnson/ released)
data.text:
Marines and sailors with 2nd Medical Battalion conducted a field exercise Sep. 21-25, 2015, on Camp Lejeune, N.C. Service members from the battalion conducted casualty evacuation drills, and assembled a shock trauma platoon. (U.S. Marine Corps video by Cpl. Ryan Young and Lance Cpl. Immanuel Johnson/ released)
